2025-12-11GACSpecial Economic Measures ActRegulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations in order to add four (4) individuals to Schedule 1 of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada, and freezing their assets unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.Registration: SOR/2025-0274 Publication Date: 2025-12-31
subject: Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations
precis: Regulations Amending the Special Economic Measures (Iran) Regulations in order to add four (4) individuals to Schedule 1 of the Regulations, prohibiting them from transacting business with individuals and businesses in Canada, and freezing their assets unless otherwise authorized by the Minister of the Foreign Affairs.
